{
    "uniqueId": "template-news-article",
    "title": "News Article",
    "description": "Single news article with hero image, content, and related links",
    "isTemplate": true,
    "language": "en",
    "layout": {
        "columns": 1,
        "rows": [
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "image",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "src": "article-hero.jpg",
                        "alt": "Article header image",
                        "objectFit": "cover"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Article Title Goes Here",
                        "level": 1
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "**Lead paragraph:** Start with a compelling introduction that summarizes the key points of your article. This should capture the reader's attention and give them a reason to continue reading.\n\nThe body of your article continues here. Write clear, engaging content that informs your readers about the topic at hand. Use short paragraphs to improve readability.\n\n## Key Points\n\nBreak up your content with subheadings to make it easier to scan. Here are some formatting options:\n\n- **Bold text** for emphasis\n- *Italic text* for titles or special terms\n- Bullet points for lists\n- Numbered lists for step-by-step instructions\n\n## More Details\n\nContinue with additional sections as needed. Include relevant information, quotes, or data that supports your story.\n\n> \"Quotes can be used to highlight important statements or testimonials from sources.\"\n\n## Conclusion\n\nWrap up your article with a summary or call-to-action. Let readers know what they should do next or what to expect in follow-up articles."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 2,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-background-hover)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "image",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "src": "article-image1.jpg",
                        "alt": "Supporting image 1",
                        "objectFit": "cover"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "*Caption: Add a description for this image*"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "image",
                        "column": 2,
                        "order": 1,
                        "src": "article-image2.jpg",
                        "alt": "Supporting image 2",
                        "objectFit": "cover"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 2,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "*Caption: Add a description for this image*"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "divider",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "style": "solid",
                        "color": "",
                        "height": "2px"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-primary-element-light)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Related Articles",
                        "level": 3
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "links",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "columns": 3,
                        "items": [
                            {
                                "title": "Related Article 1",
                                "text": "Brief description",
                                "url": "#",
                                "icon": "newspaper",
                                "target": "_self"
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Related Article 2",
                                "text": "Brief description",
                                "url": "#",
                                "icon": "newspaper",
                                "target": "_self"
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Back to News",
                                "text": "View all articles",
                                "url": "#",
                                "icon": "arrow-left",
                                "target": "_self"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "divider",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "style": "solid",
                        "color": "transparent",
                        "height": "20px"
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],
        "sideColumns": {
            "left": {
                "enabled": false,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": []
            },
            "right": {
                "enabled": false,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": []
            }
        }
    }
